{"tid":282312,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"後日去大阪，有咩要注意？","createTime":"2017-06-13T09:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T00:25:15.000Z","uid":6051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c931ad881c4d34c62694e2200bf6a7aa3e78ee16","tid":282312,"uid":6051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:14:43.000Z","msg":"同女朋友<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">同埋外母</span></span>去5日大阪 一日京都 一日奈涼 <br />\n<br />\n第一次<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">同外母</span></span>去旅行 洗唔洗買下嘢比佢加下印象分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n，佢媽咪未見過我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋想問下咁多位巴絲，我想買下衫褲日用品，一個人唱九千港幣夠唔夠（唔包酒店機票）"},{"pid":"b7dab96b6bedbe7da0cc1b032d26ae7be58a812f","tid":282312,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:15:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0181d30f0f347d4dd920e9e41019b38bf43d137e","tid":282312,"uid":1018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:17:35.000Z","msg":"你洗唔洗請外母食飯先？"},{"pid":"8540dad079a6299e10592fb96a4aa2384ac32557","tid":282312,"uid":6051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:22:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你洗唔洗請外母食飯先？</blockquote><br />\n想請下佢餐 但係我咩research都未做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢呀媽咩都plan好哂，行邊食咩⋯etc<br />\n佢呀媽仲話拎個公數袋出黎每人放5000yen做食嘢，咁就唔洗爭俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係好事定壞事"},{"pid":"7b6